Sunday 20th July 2014 ITV4
7pm to 8pm Highlights

Highlights of stage 15 a long flat stage today designed for the sprinters. Over the course of 222km, the peloton descend from 612m above sea level in Tallard, down to 46m in Nimes. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
